'''''La Vie Eco''''' ({{lang-ar|لا في إكو}}) is a weekly [[francophone]] [[Morocco|Moroccan]] independent [[newspaper]].

==History and profile==
''La Vie Éco'' was established in 1952.<ref name=men/> The weekly is based in [[Casablanca]] and is published by Media Groupe characteres,<ref name=men>{{cite web|title=Media landscape. Morocco|url=http://www.menassat.com/?q=en/media-landscape/media-landscape-11|publisher=Menasset|accessdate=9 October 2014}}</ref> a media company of the [[Akwa Group|Akwa]].<ref name="Group2012">{{cite book|title=The Report: Morocco 2012|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=fs0Fog7XneUC&pg=PA207|accessdate=9 October 2014|date=2012|publisher=Oxford Business Group|isbn=978-1-907065-54-5|page=207}}</ref>

The newspaper specializes in [[economy|economic]] and [[finance|financial]] news.<ref name=Group2012/>

